description: Recently sold: $236,000. Sharp!  Three bedroom, 2 bath, 2-story end-unit townhome in Coon Rapids, with oversized 2-car attached garage.  Walking into foyer you will notice the southern exposure of lighting shining onto the hardwood flooring through the living room, dining room and kitchen.  Sharp kitchen with cherry stained cabinets, granite counter tops, breakfast bar counter top that overlooks the dining room and living room, stainless steel refrigerator, range, microwave and dishwasher.  The upper level offers 3 bedrooms, huge family room (23x12), laundry room with upper cabinets.  The large master bedroom includes a walk in closet, six paneled doors and a walk through bath with a double vanity. Enjoy bright, sun-filled living in this end-unit home with windows on 3 sides. description:
Recently sold: $275,000. *Please note, home will be updated/renovated prior to move in. Pictures of home are current and before renovations have been started and although the home is already extremely nice they will not do justice to finished product...We are a local company that purchases homes and renovates them to a very high standard and then we rent them out as a standard rental or Rent to Own. We have many references. Home will have brand new carpet throughout, freshly painted walls, updated fixtures, modern door and cabinet hardware, refinished deck, resealed driveway and landscaping nicely cleaned up. Please keep this in mind when looking at pics and when viewing home. 

This is a beautiful 5 bed, 4 bath single family 2-Story home with finished walkout basement and located on a excellent cul-de-sac lot, home also has large fenced in backyard with playground and pond views behind. Home is 2756 sq. feet and already has many high end features such as Granite kitchen and bathroom countertops, Stainless Appliances, tile and wood laminate floors.

Upper level has 3 beds and 2 bathrooms, Master suite features master bath and large walk in closet. Main floor is Kitchen/dining/living/laundry rooms with office/5th bedroom; basement features family room with built-in entertainment center, walk out patio and large bedroom and additional full bathroom on lower level. Home as newer roof, siding, and we will be doing many renovations to the home in July which will be done prior to move in on August 1st. Property also comes with garage door opener and washer/dryer. Home also has a fully fenced backyard and nice large deck for entertaining! Home is available to move in on or possibly before 8/1/18 depending when renovations are completed. 

Rent is $2320/month but there is a $25 discount for setting up monthly electronic withdrawals making rent only $2295 after discount. Tenants responsible for gas, electric, phone/cable and fully maintaining yard by mowing yard and snow removal. 
Security Deposit is $2295 and Pet deposit is $300. Both are refundable upon move out.

Lease terms: 12 months, longer term of 2+ years is preferred. Some pets may be considered, pet deposit fee is additional $30/month per pet. ABSOLUTELY NO SMOKING AND NO SECTION 8. Great schools and excellent location near Costco, Target, Andover Movie theater & bowling alley and very close to Riverdale Shopping. Home is also close and convenient to Anoka, Maple Grove, Champlin, Coon Rapids, and Blaine, Ramsey,
